in that one notebook.

26:23.878 --> 26:24.841
Your secret notebook.

26:24.921 --> 26:26.843
My secret notebook, yeah.

26:26.923 --> 26:29.554
So will you finally just go

26:29.634 --> 26:31.181
to the Xerox place or something?

26:31.261 --> 26:34.017
