28:06.814 --> 28:09.863
I have a very strong visual style,
as you know.

28:09.943 --> 28:11.653
Yes, you... Yes, you do. Yes, you do.

28:13.238 --> 28:14.858
Yeah, definitely.

28:16.699 --> 28:19.122
Well, y-you really need this guitar?

28:19.202 --> 28:22.000
Oh, yes. And they say it's so important

28:22.080 --> 28:24.627
