28:24.707 --> 28:29.757
And, well, music, you just don't know
where it could lead.

28:29.837 --> 28:34.929
And it's only a few hundred dollars.

28:35.009 --> 28:37.307
I know it's expensive, but we can pay

28:37.387 --> 28:40.427
