and a hard case and everything.

28:52.485 --> 28:56.025
Well, I think, um, maybe...

29:00.034 --> 29:02.832
Maybe you could be, uh,
a country singer some day.

29:02.912 --> 29:03.875
- Really?
- Yeah.

29:03.955 --> 29:05.543
I wouldn't put it past you.

29:05.623 --> 29:08.213
Oh, honey, thank you!

29:08.293 --> 29:11.174
